---
// "Everything You Need" section — 6 feature cards in a 3x2 grid.
---

<section
  class="border-y border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-surface)]"
  data-reveal
  id="features"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20">
    <p class="text-center font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-blue)] mb-3">
      Platform
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-center tracking-tight">
      Everything You Need
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Batteries included — sandboxed execution, built-in tools, secure credential
      management, multi-agent delegation, and third-party integrations ship with
      every deployment.
    </p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-brand-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-brand)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="5" />
            <polyline points="5 12 12 5 19 12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">One-Click Deploy</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          <code class="font-mono text-xs">docker compose up</code> or <code class="font-mono text-xs">wrangler deploy</code> &mdash; running in minutes, not hours.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-blue-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-blue)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10" />
            <path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-2.12-9.36L23 10" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">Stateful Sessions</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Crash recovery, pause/resume, prompt caching &mdash; every turn is events-first, no data lost.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-green-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">Built-in Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          bash, read, write, web_fetch, web_search, MCP &mdash; everything an agent needs out of the box.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-brand-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-brand)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" />
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">Secure Vaults</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Credentials never enter the sandbox. Injected at the network layer by an outbound proxy.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-blue-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-blue)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
            <circle cx="19" cy="5" r="2" />
            <circle cx="5" cy="5" r="2" />
            <circle cx="5" cy="19" r="2" />
            <circle cx="19" cy="19" r="2" />
            <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="5" />
            <line x1="15" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">Multi-Agent</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Delegate sub-agents with parallel execution, per-call result aggregation, and isolated sandboxes.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article data-lift class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg)] p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)]">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-green-subtle)] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 shrink-0">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71" />
            <path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2 tracking-tight">Integrations</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Linear, GitHub, Slack out of the box. Publish agents as real teammates with their own identity.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
